Synopsis:
After the destruction of the brain, the survivors swim to shore (END_BrainBattle_DestructionOfBrain). Now, they take stock of their victory, and the burning city. 

While conversing, the githyanki depart on their red dragons. Laezel can join them or not if shes present.
Karlach leaves to die (in END_GameFinale_DeathOfKarlach). 
Towards the end of the dialogue, the party members wonder what to do next.
